      public StartEvent​(int seed, int reg, int m, double l, double pMin, double pMax, double kMin, double kMax, boolean b, double endTime, double stopT, EventQueue eventQ)
      Opens up the store and make sure new customers arrive
      Parameters:
      seed - - seed brings randomness
      reg - - cash register limit
      m - - max amount of customer in store
      l - - arrival difference signifier
      pMin - - minimum time to pick items
      pMax - - maximum time to pick items
      kMin - - minimum time to pay for items
      kMax - - maximum time to pay for items
      b - - boolean if print to console shall happen or not
      endTime - - when the store closes
      stopT - - when the simulations stops
      eventQ - - the event queue
